Description:
    Wires the app for collaborative Lexxy editing: a DocumentChannel that
    joins clients by signed GlobalID and materializes edits back into
    Action Text, the migration for the gem's update-log table, and the
    lexxy-realtime JavaScript import.

Example:
    bin/rails generate lexxy_realtime:install

    This will create:
        app/channels/document_channel.rb
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXX_create_lexxy_realtime_updates.rb
    and append `import "lexxy-realtime"` to app/javascript/application.js.
    The update-log model (LexxyRealtime::Update) ships in the gem.
